```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant user
    participant system
    participant oauth2UserService
    participant registrationAPI
    participant localRegistrationService
    participant databaseSearchService
    participant manageStatisticsTaskHandler

    user->>system: 访问插件市场 (visitPluginMarket)
    system->>databaseSearchService: 查询可用插件 (queryAvailablePlugins)
    databaseSearchService-->>system: 返回插件列表 (returnPluginList)
    system-->>user: 显示可用插件 (displayAvailablePlugins)

    user->>system: 搜索特定插件 (searchSpecificPlugin)
    system->>databaseSearchService: 搜索插件 (searchPlugin)
    databaseSearchService-->>system: 返回搜索结果 (returnSearchResults)
    system-->>user: 显示搜索结果 (displaySearchResults)

    user->>system: 选择插件 (selectPlugin)
    system-->>user: 显示插件详情 (displayPluginDetails)

    user->>system: 下载插件 (downloadPlugin)
    system->>localRegistrationService: 获取下载链接 (getDownloadLink)
    localRegistrationService-->>system: 提供下载链接 (provideDownloadLink)
    system-->>user: 提供下载链接 (provideDownloadLink)

    user->>system: 安装插件 (installPlugin)
    system-->>user: 确认安装 (confirmInstallation)

    user->>system: 使用OAuth登录(GitHub) (loginWithOAuth)
    system->>oauth2UserService: 重定向到GitHub进行身份验证 (redirectToGitHub)
    oauth2UserService->>GitHub: 认证 (authenticate)
    GitHub-->>oauth2UserService: 带令牌重定向回来 (redirectWithToken)
    oauth2UserService-->>system: 确认登录 (confirmLogin)
    system-->>user: 显示用户仪表板 (displayUserDashboard)

    user->>system: 发布新插件 (publishNewPlugin)
    system->>registrationAPI: 提供插件上传界面 (provideUploadInterface)
    registrationAPI->>localRegistrationService: 上传插件包 (uploadPluginPackage)
    localRegistrationService-->>registrationAPI: 验证并存储插件 (verifyAndStorePlugin)
    registrationAPI-->>system: 确认插件发布 (confirmPluginPublish)
    system-->>user: 显示已发布插件详情 (displayPublishedPluginDetails)

    user->>system: 确认插件发布 (confirmPluginPublish)
    system->>manageStatisticsTaskHandler: 更新统计数据 (updateStatistics)
    manageStatisticsTaskHandler-->>system: 确认更新 (confirmUpdate)
    system-->>user: 显示更新后的统计数据 (displayUpdatedStatistics)
```
